00:25:54.421 --> 00:26:00.268
over by a Gowym in terms of kingship.

00:26:00.768 --> 00:26:03.451
They wanted to follow in the ways of

00:26:03.490 --> 00:26:06.474
the goy and they chose Sha'uwl,

00:26:06.875 --> 00:26:09.258
who is the prototype for the Sha'uwl that

00:26:09.337 --> 00:26:10.779
wrote the Christian New Testament.

00:26:12.080 --> 00:26:12.942
And so

00:26:14.192 --> 00:26:18.494
Sha'uwl or Shamuw’el comes to Yahowah and said,

00:26:19.035 --> 00:26:19.894
I have let you down.

00:26:21.076 --> 00:26:22.016
I have failed you.

00:26:23.136 --> 00:26:25.297
I'm trying to guide the people as a

00:26:25.356 --> 00:26:26.998
Shaphat, as a judge,

00:26:27.117 --> 00:26:29.398
one exercising good judgment.

00:26:29.959 --> 00:26:32.019
And they have chosen to reject what I'm

00:26:32.059 --> 00:26:34.881
doing and to choose a king in the

00:26:34.921 --> 00:26:39.123
style of the Gentiles.

00:26:39.163 --> 00:26:39.962
Then Yahowah says, no,

00:26:39.982 --> 00:26:41.022
they haven't reject you.

00:26:41.042 --> 00:26:42.544
They're rejecting me.

00:26:43.367 --> 00:26:45.868
My people are rejecting me.

00:26:45.909 --> 00:26:49.111
They've been doing it ever since they were

00:26:49.151 --> 00:26:51.471
conceived as Yisrael,

00:26:52.211 --> 00:26:59.115
going back to Abraham and Yitschaq and

00:26:59.155 --> 00:26:59.576
Jacob.

00:27:00.876 --> 00:27:01.876
And thereafter,

00:27:01.916 --> 00:27:03.758
particularly during the Exodus,

00:27:03.778 --> 00:27:05.159
where they were completely obnoxious.

00:27:06.519 --> 00:27:08.559
But it is interesting because, of course,

00:27:08.880 --> 00:27:11.801
not only did Yahowah at that time

00:27:13.222 --> 00:27:15.766
give us twelve reasons that we should not

00:27:15.806 --> 00:27:16.506
be political.

00:27:16.685 --> 00:27:19.148
God is exceedingly anti-political.

00:27:19.689 --> 00:27:24.974
He told Shamuw’el to tell the Israelites

00:27:25.255 --> 00:27:27.596
that by choosing a king in the style

00:27:27.777 --> 00:27:30.440
of Gentile nations to rule over them,

00:27:30.920 --> 00:27:32.281
these are the twelve things that are going

00:27:32.301 --> 00:27:33.041
to happen to you,

00:27:33.102 --> 00:27:35.023
and they're all horrible.

00:27:35.525 --> 00:27:36.346
And it talks about

00:27:37.590 --> 00:27:39.551
them doing the very things that we see

00:27:39.592 --> 00:27:42.053
Donald Trump doing now,

00:27:42.073 --> 00:27:44.753
getting a group of people around him that

00:27:45.375 --> 00:27:47.435
he bribes and who bribe him,

00:27:47.796 --> 00:27:51.718
and that they work as a collective whole

00:27:51.778 --> 00:27:55.199
to advance their fuhrer's,

00:27:55.239 --> 00:27:56.140
the leader's agenda.

00:27:57.790 --> 00:28:00.973
And it's done entirely through dishonesty

00:28:01.013 --> 00:28:01.493
and bribes.

00:28:02.035 --> 00:28:03.556
Then he says he's going to steal your

00:28:03.615 --> 00:28:05.817
sons and is going to use them for

00:28:05.897 --> 00:28:09.480
war because he wants to covet what belongs

00:28:09.500 --> 00:28:12.022
to others, a la Donald Trump.

00:28:13.483 --> 00:28:15.486
He then says he's going to tax you.

00:28:17.386 --> 00:28:19.709
Take Trump's tariffs, for example,

00:28:20.189 --> 00:28:25.193
and take from you your wealth because he

00:28:25.233 --> 00:28:25.574
wants it.

00:28:26.567 --> 00:28:29.990
Then it says that he will use what

00:28:30.010 --> 00:28:32.433
he steals from you and your productivity

00:28:33.454 --> 00:28:38.220
to build ever more warm machines.

00:28:38.299 --> 00:28:40.623
And then he will use your sons to

00:28:40.663 --> 00:28:41.063
drive them.

00:28:42.044 --> 00:28:45.248
And it goes on and on talking about

00:28:45.347 --> 00:28:45.607
what...

00:28:46.617 --> 00:28:48.118
human governance brings.

00:28:48.378 --> 00:28:51.059
And it describes what we're witnessing

00:28:51.519 --> 00:28:53.181
today and we've witnessed all through

00:28:53.260 --> 00:28:56.061
human civilized history.

00:28:56.742 --> 00:28:59.743
So that's a way of introducing Romans

00:28:59.784 --> 00:29:03.465
because it says the opposite of what God

00:29:03.486 --> 00:29:03.645
says.

00:29:03.705 --> 00:29:05.405
It's one of the reasons you can say

00:29:05.445 --> 00:29:06.287
for certain

00:29:07.365 --> 00:29:08.888
that Paul did not speak for God.

00:29:09.189 --> 00:29:12.174
So he was speaking either for himself or

00:29:12.214 --> 00:29:13.155
for another spirit.

00:29:13.616 --> 00:29:15.519
And since he acknowledges the spirit that

00:29:15.539 --> 00:29:18.345
he was speaking for in the final chapter

00:29:18.385 --> 00:29:20.368
of second Corinthians, being Satan,

00:29:21.501 --> 00:29:22.823
It's not hard to figure out how we

00:29:22.863 --> 00:29:24.604
came up with this notion.

00:29:25.223 --> 00:29:26.825
So in this particular discussion,

00:29:26.884 --> 00:29:28.707
it begins in clever fashion,

00:29:28.946 --> 00:29:31.748
although in an arrogant and condescending

00:29:31.788 --> 00:29:32.108
manner.

00:29:32.588 --> 00:29:35.069
It deploys the logical fallacy known as

00:29:35.130 --> 00:29:36.530
the straw man.

00:29:37.251 --> 00:29:38.051
Before I share it,

00:29:38.152 --> 00:29:40.054
it's important that you know that the

00:29:40.114 --> 00:29:42.474
Towrah provides very few instructions

00:29:42.555 --> 00:29:43.816
regarding marriage.

00:29:45.042 --> 00:29:46.523
because that's the straw man he's going to

00:29:46.564 --> 00:29:47.243
base this on.

00:29:48.003 --> 00:29:50.325
It reveals that men and women come

00:29:50.365 --> 00:29:53.945
together and they do so to bear and

00:29:53.986 --> 00:29:54.566
raise children.

00:29:55.247 --> 00:29:57.686
There is no description of marriage in the

00:29:57.727 --> 00:29:59.188
Towrah.

00:29:59.208 --> 00:30:01.489
There is no marriage vows in the Towrah.

00:30:02.128 --> 00:30:04.430
There's no tokens of a marriage like a

00:30:04.589 --> 00:30:07.651
ceremony or a ring in the Towrah.

00:30:07.951 --> 00:30:09.811
There is no until death do we part

00:30:09.912 --> 00:30:10.412
in the Towrah.

00:30:11.499 --> 00:30:13.000
Matter of fact, the Towrah says,

00:30:13.079 --> 00:30:14.240
if you don't like each other,

00:30:14.279 --> 00:30:15.740
you write a letter and you're separated

00:30:15.800 --> 00:30:16.441
and it's all done.

00:30:17.080 --> 00:30:18.102
Just write a letter, say, you know,

00:30:18.162 --> 00:30:19.761
I'm not happy with you anymore and it's

00:30:19.862 --> 00:30:20.623
over, go away.

00:30:21.323 --> 00:30:23.483
So God's got no issue with divorce.

00:30:25.364 --> 00:30:27.345
Spiritual divorce, religious divorce,

00:30:27.505 --> 00:30:28.305
different story.

00:30:28.625 --> 00:30:31.626
Religious adultery, yeah, that's not good.

00:30:32.425 --> 00:30:36.769
God has nothing to say about promiscuity

00:30:36.888 --> 00:30:40.912
or sexual relations in or out of marriage

00:30:40.951 --> 00:30:43.034
because there is no definition of

00:30:43.773 --> 00:30:44.134
marriage.

00:30:44.273 --> 00:30:46.895
Nor does he give two hoots whether or

00:30:46.935 --> 00:30:50.159
not you have one spouse or ten spouses.

00:30:50.638 --> 00:30:51.298
Doesn't care.

00:30:52.059 --> 00:30:53.721
Those are the things that the religious

00:30:53.740 --> 00:30:54.602
are obsessed about.

00:30:54.682 --> 00:30:55.281
That is correct.

00:30:55.301 --> 00:30:57.584
That is all a religious concoction,

00:30:58.624 --> 00:31:01.405
largely as a result of the imposition of

00:31:01.445 --> 00:31:02.086
Christianity.

00:31:03.116 --> 00:31:05.338
So it reveals that men and women simply

00:31:05.598 --> 00:31:07.820
come together to bear and raise children.

00:31:08.040 --> 00:31:10.884
That's our purpose if we wish to be

00:31:11.223 --> 00:31:11.724
married.

00:31:11.744 --> 00:31:13.767
I speak of Leah as my wife,

00:31:14.067 --> 00:31:16.048
not because of some ceremony,

00:31:16.449 --> 00:31:17.750
not because of some ring,

00:31:18.050 --> 00:31:19.811
not because of some vows,

00:31:20.192 --> 00:31:23.134
but because we are together as a family.

00:31:23.214 --> 00:31:24.957
We live together as family.

00:31:25.156 --> 00:31:27.178
which you would describe as husband and

00:31:27.218 --> 00:31:27.498
wife.

00:31:27.597 --> 00:31:30.079
We love one another and we have built

00:31:30.180 --> 00:31:32.040
this home together and we work

00:31:32.101 --> 00:31:35.501
cooperatively together as part of Yahowah's

00:31:35.561 --> 00:31:36.303
covenant family.

00:31:36.643 --> 00:31:39.523
And our children happen to be members of

00:31:39.544 --> 00:31:40.525
the covenant family.

00:31:41.788 --> 00:31:42.809
Now, while it speaks,

00:31:43.450 --> 00:31:45.432
Yahowah does in the Towrah about adultery,

00:31:45.832 --> 00:31:47.753
it is not in the sense of having

00:31:47.874 --> 00:31:50.695
more than one wife or husband.

00:31:51.476 --> 00:31:53.617
It is instead that God does not want

00:31:53.678 --> 00:31:57.601
us to be whoring around with false gods.

00:31:57.661 --> 00:31:58.061
Further,

00:31:58.422 --> 00:32:01.104
while the Towrah speaks against incest,

00:32:01.163 --> 00:32:04.026
pedophilia, rape, bestiality,

00:32:04.686 --> 00:32:05.846
and prostitution,

00:32:07.269 --> 00:32:11.112
it does not say anything about sex outside

00:32:11.152 --> 00:32:11.652
of marriage.

00:32:14.769 --> 00:32:17.171
There is some guidance regarding a woman's

00:32:17.611 --> 00:32:18.511
menstrual period,

00:32:18.692 --> 00:32:20.732
and it's because of her health,

00:32:20.913 --> 00:32:22.013
both mental health,

00:32:22.713 --> 00:32:24.894
and because it can be a little bit

00:32:24.934 --> 00:32:26.115
of a crabby period,

00:32:26.556 --> 00:32:28.636
and not the woman's fault.

00:32:28.696 --> 00:32:30.817
It's just a little separation during that

00:32:30.857 --> 00:32:33.679
period, a little kindness in that regard.

00:32:33.699 --> 00:32:34.819
It's probably a good thing.

00:32:34.859 --> 00:32:35.680
You go to your tent,

00:32:35.700 --> 00:32:38.020
he stays in his tent during that period,

00:32:38.121 --> 00:32:40.102
and you don't want the blood going...

00:32:40.241 --> 00:32:41.623
I don't want to go back into the...

00:32:45.184 --> 00:32:46.585
physiological issues here,

00:32:46.625 --> 00:32:49.445
but God gives some wise advice.

00:32:50.567 --> 00:32:52.166
And he says also,

00:32:52.267 --> 00:32:54.387
you must be compassionate to a slave

00:32:54.407 --> 00:32:54.627
woman.

00:32:54.667 --> 00:32:56.888
You cannot treat a woman like she is

00:32:56.909 --> 00:32:58.568
just a sex object for you to rape.

00:32:59.509 --> 00:33:00.910
As for divorce, as I mentioned,

00:33:00.970 --> 00:33:02.849
it is simple as writing a letter and

00:33:03.130 --> 00:33:03.631
separating.

00:33:04.270 --> 00:33:06.811
The lone rule regarding divorce says that

00:33:06.832 --> 00:33:09.071
a woman remarries and divorces again,

00:33:09.412 --> 00:33:11.232
the first husband cannot have her back.

00:33:11.977 --> 00:33:12.517
Beyond this,

00:33:12.597 --> 00:33:16.000
there is a non-binding recommendation on

00:33:16.101 --> 00:33:19.063
how a man can assist his brother's widow

00:33:19.584 --> 00:33:22.226
in the case of a childless marriage.

00:33:22.246 --> 00:33:23.926
Now, against that backdrop,

00:33:24.667 --> 00:33:28.991
Sha'uwl Paul opined, or alternatively,

00:33:29.451 --> 00:33:31.574
are you presently ignorant, brothers?

00:33:32.575 --> 00:33:33.955
Knowing and understanding

00:33:34.844 --> 00:33:36.184
than the Towrah,

00:33:36.765 --> 00:33:38.165
he's claiming to be an expert on the

00:33:38.205 --> 00:33:38.506
Towrah.

00:33:39.227 --> 00:33:40.487
He's not.

00:33:40.807 --> 00:33:44.429
I say that the Towrah is like a

00:33:44.529 --> 00:33:49.571
Lord and master ruling over the man for

00:33:50.373 --> 00:33:54.115
however long and to whatever degree that

00:33:54.154 --> 00:33:54.694
he lives.

00:33:55.836 --> 00:33:57.057
This is Paul's theme.

00:33:57.914 --> 00:34:00.375
The Towrah is a cruel taskmaster.

00:34:00.455 --> 00:34:01.875
It's a lord.

00:34:01.915 --> 00:34:02.395
It's a master.

00:34:02.596 --> 00:34:03.676
What's amazing, of course,

00:34:03.696 --> 00:34:06.436
is he will call his man-god a lord.

00:34:06.817 --> 00:34:08.097
Doesn't seem the conflict in that.

00:34:08.217 --> 00:34:09.518
Using the same word, by the way,

00:34:09.838 --> 00:34:11.438
by derivation of curios.

00:34:11.878 --> 00:34:16.719
So he'll call his mythical god-man a lord.

00:34:16.800 --> 00:34:19.780
But when it comes to the Towrah,

00:34:19.960 --> 00:34:20.880
lord is bad.

00:34:20.960 --> 00:34:22.961
When it comes to his mythical god-man,

00:34:23.001 --> 00:34:23.561
lord is good.

00:34:24.376 --> 00:34:24.737
Now,

00:34:24.757 --> 00:34:28.177
I would call that a fallacy or hypocrisy

00:34:28.197 --> 00:34:29.538
or whatever you want to call it.

00:34:29.938 --> 00:34:30.378
But anyway,

00:34:30.438 --> 00:34:33.818
his idea is that Towrah bad because it

00:34:33.878 --> 00:34:34.699
lords over people.

00:34:35.119 --> 00:34:37.199
What he's inferring is that the Towrah is

00:34:37.300 --> 00:34:38.121
a book of laws.

00:34:38.320 --> 00:34:43.081
But if you read God's definition of Towrah,

00:34:44.121 --> 00:34:46.922
he says it's based upon the verb yara.

00:34:48.163 --> 00:34:49.744
Yara does not mean law.

00:34:49.764 --> 00:34:50.443
Doesn't mean laws.

00:34:51.400 --> 00:34:53.320
It means guidance, teaching, inspection,

00:34:54.282 --> 00:34:55.802
instructions, and directions.

00:34:57.242 --> 00:34:57.862
Those aren't laws.

00:34:58.943 --> 00:35:00.664
The Towrah is not comprised of laws.

00:35:01.125 --> 00:35:02.365
It does not lord over.

00:35:02.706 --> 00:35:03.106
In fact,

00:35:03.465 --> 00:35:04.786
you know how many Hebrew words there are

00:35:04.806 --> 00:35:05.427
for obey?

00:35:06.347 --> 00:35:06.807
Zero.

00:35:07.108 --> 00:35:07.449
Zero.

00:35:07.648 --> 00:35:09.068
Not a single Hebrew word for obey.

00:35:09.769 --> 00:35:12.811
The word that is rendered obey in your

00:35:12.990 --> 00:35:16.552
Bible is shema, and it means to listen.

00:35:18.454 --> 00:35:18.753
Sorry.

00:35:19.335 --> 00:35:19.375
So,

00:35:21.054 --> 00:35:23.197
He has misrepresented the Towrah from the

00:35:23.277 --> 00:35:23.677
onset.

00:35:23.858 --> 00:35:26.601
The Towrah is a means of teaching and

00:35:26.641 --> 00:35:27.340
guiding us.

00:35:27.981 --> 00:35:30.443
What Yahowah says about the Towrah is that

00:35:30.664 --> 00:35:32.286
you either will observe my Towrah and

00:35:32.326 --> 00:35:34.469
capitalize on what I am teaching and

00:35:34.509 --> 00:35:35.750
guiding you on my Towrah,

00:35:36.871 --> 00:35:38.693
or you're not going to live.

00:35:39.679 --> 00:35:40.721
It is the source of life.

00:35:41.001 --> 00:35:41.902
He gave you a life.

00:35:42.184 --> 00:35:43.666
You can choose to ignore the Towrah.

00:35:43.686 --> 00:35:44.929
You can do what Paul did and demean

00:35:44.949 --> 00:35:45.369
the Towrah.

00:35:45.811 --> 00:35:46.913
But if you do so,

00:35:47.233 --> 00:35:49.938
then you have squandered the gifts of the

00:35:49.978 --> 00:35:50.360
Towrah,

00:35:50.760 --> 00:35:51.461
which are

00:35:52.284 --> 00:35:54.626
the covenant and the ability to live

00:35:54.666 --> 00:35:57.047
beyond your mortal existence and enter

00:35:57.086 --> 00:35:57.748
God's presence.

00:35:58.108 --> 00:35:59.929
So if you forego that,

00:35:59.969 --> 00:36:02.150
if you speak against the plan that God

00:36:02.210 --> 00:36:06.974
has articulated that will reconcile our

00:36:07.034 --> 00:36:09.615
relationship, make us immortal,

00:36:10.777 --> 00:36:11.657
not guilty,

00:36:12.097 --> 00:36:13.938
adopted into his covenant family,

00:36:14.039 --> 00:36:16.141
enriched and empowered through the

00:36:16.201 --> 00:36:17.342
covenant, the Beryth,

00:36:17.681 --> 00:36:19.023
through the Mowedym,

00:36:19.063 --> 00:36:21.045
the restoring witnesses to the eternal

00:36:21.065 --> 00:36:23.186
testimony and these annual appointments,

00:36:23.827 --> 00:36:25.688
should you capitalize upon them,

00:36:26.108 --> 00:36:28.411
you will live forever and you are

00:36:28.630 --> 00:36:29.172
liberated.

00:36:29.211 --> 00:36:31.193
The very first thing that God says on

00:36:31.233 --> 00:36:33.675
the first item that he etched on the

00:36:33.795 --> 00:36:38.119
first tablet of stone is that he's a

00:36:38.179 --> 00:36:38.619
liberator.

00:36:40.608 --> 00:36:43.331
The first thing he says about when he

00:36:43.471 --> 00:36:46.574
returns and there are no more religious

00:36:46.614 --> 00:36:47.614
people on the planet,

00:36:47.775 --> 00:36:50.257
that he will never have to hear the

00:36:50.297 --> 00:36:51.318
title Lord again.

00:36:52.438 --> 00:36:54.041
He hates it.

00:36:55.902 --> 00:36:57.342
Yahowah is a liberator.

00:36:57.463 --> 00:37:00.306
He is not a master or oppressor.

00:37:00.947 --> 00:37:04.929
Yahowah is the father to the covenant

00:37:04.949 --> 00:37:05.429
family.

00:37:05.871 --> 00:37:07.793
He is not a Lord.

00:37:08.768 --> 00:37:10.969
Towrah is not to be obeyed.

00:37:11.130 --> 00:37:12.809
It is to be observed.

00:37:12.909 --> 00:37:17.231
It is to be listened to.

00:37:17.351 --> 00:37:18.711
It provides instructions.

00:37:19.652 --> 00:37:22.592
So Paul's premise is that the Towrah is

00:37:22.652 --> 00:37:25.213
like the Lord and master ruling over the

00:37:25.273 --> 00:37:28.235
man for however long and whatever degree

00:37:28.275 --> 00:37:29.916
he lives.

00:37:30.356 --> 00:37:30.615
Wrong.

00:37:31.994 --> 00:37:33.014
Just flat out wrong.

00:37:33.554 --> 00:37:34.355
Romans seven one.

00:37:35.074 --> 00:37:36.335
This is called a straw man.

00:37:36.755 --> 00:37:41.177
He has created a mythical construct that

00:37:41.237 --> 00:37:41.797
isn't true.

00:37:41.938 --> 00:37:45.679
And from the false creation,

00:37:46.099 --> 00:37:47.840
he's then going to present an argument.

00:37:47.981 --> 00:37:51.342
That means that the argument is fallacious

00:37:51.722 --> 00:37:53.422
no matter what he says from this point

00:37:53.503 --> 00:37:56.784
on, because he has erected a straw man.

00:37:58.188 --> 00:38:00.449
Now, the Romans were hardly ignorant,

00:38:00.590 --> 00:38:03.711
but since they knew almost nothing about

00:38:03.771 --> 00:38:04.271
